Teach me.
I want you to teach me.

158
00:12:19,004 --> 00:12:21,472
- I tried to teach you.
- I read your book.

159
00:12:21,540 --> 00:12:23,474
- You don't understand it.
- No.

160
00:12:23,542 --> 00:12:25,100
Perhaps it's not well written.

161
00:12:25,177 --> 00:12:27,737
No, no.
I want to understand it.

162
00:12:27,813 --> 00:12:29,474
