to know something.

176
00:13:03,716 --> 00:13:06,514
What do they say?
To get on in the world.

177
00:13:06,585 --> 00:13:09,019
How can I do that if I fail?

178
00:13:09,088 --> 00:13:10,521
But I don't understand.

179
00:13:10,589 --> 00:13:13,023
I don't understand
what anything means.

180
00:13:13,092 --> 00:13:14,821
And I walk around
from morning till night...

181
00:13:14,894 --> 00:13:17,226
with this one thought
in my head... I'm stupid.

182
00:13:17,296 --> 00:13:18,729
No one thinks you're stupid.

183
00:13:18,798 --> 00:13:22,029
- What am I, then?
- I think you're angry.

184
00:13:24,103 --> 00:13:26,367
Many people are.

185
00:13:27,406 --> 00:13:29,499
I have an appointment
I have to make...

186
00:13:29,575 --> 00:13:31,668
