a previously scheduled meeting.

190
00:13:37,416 --> 00:13:39,077
You think I'm nothing.

191
00:13:39,151 --> 00:13:41,415
I have an appointment
with a realtor and my wife.

192
00:13:41,487 --> 00:13:43,751
- You think I'm stupid.
- No, I certainly do not.

193
00:13:43,823 --> 00:13:46,587
- You said it. You did.
- When? No, I never did.

194
00:13:46,659 --> 00:13:49,093
Or never would say that
to a student.

195
00:13:49,161 --> 00:13:51,994
You said,
"What can that mean?"

196
00:13:52,064 --> 00:13:54,828
"What can that mean?"

197
00:13:54,900 --> 00:13:56,162
What did that mean to you?

198
00:13:56,235 --> 00:13:58,066
