- How people learn.

246
00:15:42,608 --> 00:15:44,041
How I could learn.

247
00:15:44,109 --> 00:15:46,509
Which is what
I've been speaking of in class.

248
00:15:46,578 --> 00:15:48,808
And, of course,
you can't hear it, Carol.

249
00:15:48,881 --> 00:15:50,542
Of course you can't.

250
00:15:50,616 --> 00:15:53,551
If you are told...
Listen to this...

251
00:15:53,619 --> 00:15:57,555
If the young child is told
that he cannot understand...

252
00:15:57,623 --> 00:16:00,490
then he takes it
as a description of himself.

253
00:16:00,559 --> 00:16:01,992
What am I?

254
00:16:02,061 --> 00:16:04,495
I am that
which cannot understand.

