00:16:04,563 --> 00:16:06,428
And I saw you back there...

256
00:16:06,498 --> 00:16:07,795
when we were speaking
of the concept...

257
00:16:07,866 --> 00:16:10,198
I can't understand any of them.

258
00:16:10,269 --> 00:16:12,203
Then that's my fault.

259
00:16:12,271 --> 00:16:16,207
That is not your fault.
And that is not verbiage.

260
00:16:16,275 --> 00:16:20,211
That is what I firmly hold
