Through my life.

271
00:16:42,501 --> 00:16:43,934
In my childhood.

272
00:16:44,003 --> 00:16:46,164
Perhaps they stopped,
but I heard them continue.

273
00:16:46,238 --> 00:16:47,728
And what did they say?

274
00:16:47,806 --> 00:16:50,934
