287
00:17:27,646 --> 00:17:29,204
"Why was I born?

288
00:17:29,281 --> 00:17:31,749
"How deluded are those
who put their trust in me?"

289
00:17:31,817 --> 00:17:34,513
Et cetera and so on.
And he crashes the plane.

290
00:17:34,586 --> 00:17:37,646
- He could just...
- That's right.

291
00:17:37,723 --> 00:17:39,020
"My attention
wandered for a moment."

292
00:17:39,091 --> 00:17:42,288
"I had a thought
I did not like, but now..."

293
00:17:42,361 --> 00:17:43,555
That's what I'm telling you.

294
00:17:43,629 --> 00:17:45,859
"It's time
to put my attention..."

295
00:17:45,931 --> 00:17:47,796
You see, it is not...

296
00:17:47,866 --> 00:17:49,857
