299
00:17:54,907 --> 00:17:57,034
And you will think,
"Why was I born...

300
00:17:57,109 --> 00:17:58,667
"to be the laughingstock
of a world...

301
00:17:58,744 --> 00:18:00,473
"in which everyone
is better than I...

302
00:18:00,546 --> 00:18:02,241
