00:19:19,458 --> 00:19:22,256
I've... Look.

334
00:19:22,327 --> 00:19:24,192
The sooner I get off,
the sooner I'll be down.

335
00:19:24,263 --> 00:19:27,892
Isn't that evident?
I love you.

336
00:19:27,966 --> 00:19:31,402
Listen... Listen.
I said I love you.

337
00:19:31,470 --> 00:19:33,961
It's going to work out
