338
00:19:34,039 --> 00:19:36,473
Because I feel that it is.

339
00:19:36,542 --> 00:19:38,976
All right,
I'll be right down.

340
00:19:39,044 --> 00:19:41,308
Yes, all right, I did.

341
00:19:41,380 --> 00:19:44,577
