- With my wife. With work.

369
00:21:23,015 --> 00:21:24,539
Tell me.

370
00:21:30,489 --> 00:21:33,014
Would you like a cup of tea?

371
00:22:08,794 --> 00:22:13,891
As I was saying,
I came late to teaching.

372
00:22:13,965 --> 00:22:16,433
And I found it artificial...

373
00:22:16,501 --> 00:22:20,460
the notion of
