374
00:22:20,539 --> 00:22:23,099
I told you, I hated school.

375
00:22:23,175 --> 00:22:25,006
I hated teachers.

376
00:22:25,077 --> 00:22:27,409
I hated anyone who was
in a position of a boss...

377
00:22:27,479 --> 00:22:30,915
because I knew...
I didn't think, mind you...

378
00:22:30,982 --> 00:22:33,416
I knew I was going to fail.

379
00:22:33,485 --> 00:22:36,181
Late in life,
when I got out from under...

380
00:22:36,254 --> 00:22:39,587
when I worked my way out
of the need to fail...

381
00:22:39,658 --> 00:22:41,319
How do you do that?

382
00:22:41,393 --> 00:22:43,452
I'm going to tell you.

383
00:22:43,528 --> 00:22:45,257
You have to look
at what you are...

384
00:22:45,330 --> 00:22:48,060
