of myself as a failure...

392
00:23:05,817 --> 00:23:08,945
perhaps I should begin
by succeeding now and again.

393
00:23:09,020 --> 00:23:12,581
Look. The tests, you see...

394
00:23:12,657 --> 00:23:15,922
which you encounter
in school...

395
00:23:15,994 --> 00:23:18,087
in college, in life...

396
00:23:18,163 --> 00:23:21,929
were designed for idiots
by idiots.

397
00:23:22,000 --> 00:23:23,831
There's no need to fail at them.

398
00:23:23,902 --> 00:23:25,426
They're not
a test of your worth.

399
00:23:25,504 --> 00:23:27,165
They are a test of
your ability...

400
00:23:27,239 --> 00:23:29,537
to retain and spout back
misinformation.

401
00:23:29,608 --> 00:23:32,543
Of course you fail them.
They're nonsense.

402
00:23:32,611 --> 00:23:34,977
No. No.

403
00:23:35,046 --> 00:23:37,879
Yes. They're garbage.

404
00:23:37,949 --> 00:23:39,075
They're a joke.

405
00:23:39,151 --> 00:23:41,051
How can you say that?

406
00:23:41,119 --> 00:23:44,054
Look at me.

407
00:23:44,122 --> 00:23:45,555
The tenure committee.

408
00:23:45,624 --> 00:23:48,559
The tenure committee
come to judge me.

409
00:23:48,627 --> 00:23:50,595
The bad tenure committee.

410
00:23:50,662 --> 00:23:52,687
The test. You see?

411
00:23:52,764 --> 00:23:54,595
They put me to the test.

412
00:23:54,666 --> 00:23:55,826
They had people
voting on me...

413
00:23:55,901 --> 00:23:57,926
I wouldn't
employ to wax my car.

414
00:23:58,003 --> 00:24:01,063
And yet I go before
the great tenure committee...

415
00:24:01,139 --> 00:24:04,131
I have an urge to vomit...

416
00:24:04,209 --> 00:24:08,407
