Oh, no. They announced it.

420
00:24:15,887 --> 00:24:17,912
But they haven't signed.

421
00:24:17,989 --> 00:24:20,787
You see? At any moment.

422
00:24:21,827 --> 00:24:23,260
They might not sign.

423
00:24:23,328 --> 00:24:26,991
The house might not go through.

424
00:24:28,934 --> 00:24:31,698
They'll find out my dark secret.

425
00:24:31,770 --> 00:24:32,930
What is it?

426
00:24:35,006 --> 00:24:37,668
There isn't one.

427
00:24:37,742 --> 00:24:40,677
But they'll find
an index of my badness.

428
00:24:40,745 --> 00:24:43,942
- Index?
- A pointer.

429
00:24:44,015 --> 00:24:46,813
A pointer. You see?

430
00:24:46,885 --> 00:24:48,409
You see?

431
