- No.

440
00:25:22,387 --> 00:25:24,617
And I apologize.

441
00:25:24,689 --> 00:25:27,852
Of course you want to know
about your grade.

442
00:25:27,926 --> 00:25:29,951
Of course you can't
concentrate on any...

