- I'll make you a deal.

445
00:25:37,602 --> 00:25:39,536
You have to take the call.

446
00:25:39,604 --> 00:25:41,037
Let it ring.
I'll make you a deal.

447
00:25:41,106 --> 00:25:42,266
You stay here.

448
00:25:42,340 --> 00:25:44,035
I'm going to say... Stay here.

449
00:25:44,109 --> 00:25:47,044
I'm going to say
it was not you...

