no particular order...

778
00:44:33,637 --> 00:44:37,437
and I would like
to share them with you.

779
00:44:37,508 --> 00:44:41,342
That I would pursue it...

780
00:44:41,412 --> 00:44:43,437
that I desired it...

781
00:44:43,514 --> 00:44:46,449
that I was not pure of longing
for security...

782
00:44:46,517 --> 00:44:49,884
and that perhaps
was not reprehensible in me.

783
00:44:49,953 --> 00:44:52,251
That I had duties
beyond the school...

784
00:44:52,322 --> 00:44:54,722
and that my duty to my home,
for instance...

785
00:44:54,792 --> 00:44:56,589
was, or should be
if it were not...

786
00:44:56,660 --> 00:44:58,287
of an equal weight.

787
00:44:58,362 --> 00:45:03,026
That tenure and security
and, yes, and comfort...

788
00:45:03,100 --> 00:45:05,364
were not of themselves
to be scorned...

789
00:45:05,436 --> 00:45:08,894
and were even worthy
of honorable pursuit.

790
00:45:08,972 --> 00:45:11,065
And that it was given me...

791
00:45:11,141 --> 00:45:13,666
here in this place
which I enjoy...

792
00:45:13,744 --> 00:45:16,645
and in which I find comfort
to assure myself...

793
00:45:16,714 --> 00:45:19,911
of, as far as it rests
in the material...

794
00:45:19,983 --> 00:45:23,419
a continuation
of that comfort and joy.

795
00:45:23,487 --> 00:45:25,421
In exchange for what?

796
00:45:25,489 --> 00:45:28,981
Teaching... which I love.

797
00:45:32,996 --> 00:45:35,931
What was the price
of this security?

798
00:45:35,999 --> 00:45:38,934
To obtain tenure,
which tenure...

799
00:45:39,002 --> 00:45:41,061
the committee is in the process
of granting me...

800
00:45:41,138 --> 00:45:42,537
and on the basis of which...

801
00:45:42,606 --> 00:45:46,235
I contracted
to purchase a house.

802
00:45:49,012 --> 00:45:50,946
Now.

803
00:45:51,014 --> 00:45:53,983
As you don't have
your own family at this point...

804
00:45:54,051 --> 00:45:55,951
you may not know
what that means...

805
00:45:56,019 --> 00:45:58,453
but to me,
it is very important...

806
00:45:58,522 --> 00:46:02,390
a home, a good home,
to raise my family.

807
00:46:02,459 --> 00:46:04,393
Now, the tenure committee
will meet.

808
00:46:04,461 --> 00:46:06,520
This is the process...

809
00:46:06,597 --> 00:46:08,895
and a good process,
under which...

810
00:46:08,966 --> 00:46:11,901
the school has functioned
for quite a long time.

811
00:46:11,969 --> 00:46:14,904
They will meet
and hear your complaint...

812
00:46:14,972 --> 00:46:16,906
which you have
the right to make...

813
00:46:16,974 --> 00:46:18,874
and they will dismiss it.

814
00:46:18,942 --> 00:46:21,376
They will dismiss
your complaint...

815
00:46:21,445 --> 00:46:23,379
and in
the intervening period...

816
00:46:23,447 --> 00:46:26,245
I will lose my house.

817
00:46:26,316 --> 00:46:28,409
I will not be able
to close on my house.

818
00:46:28,485 --> 00:46:30,419
I will lose my deposit.

819
00:46:30,487 --> 00:46:34,423
And the home I picked out
for my wife and son...

820
00:46:34,491 --> 00:46:36,959
will go by the boards.

821
00:46:37,027 --> 00:46:39,962
I see that I have angered you.

822
00:46:40,030 --> 00:46:41,930
I understand
your anger with teachers.

823
00:46:41,999 --> 00:46:43,933
I was angry with mine.

824
00:46:44,001 --> 00:46:46,561
I felt hurt
and humiliated by them...

825
00:46:46,637 --> 00:46:49,037
which is one of the reasons
I went into education.

826
00:46:49,106 --> 00:46:51,472
What do you want of me?

827
00:46:53,010 --> 00:46:55,342
I was hurt when
I received the report...

828
00:46:55,412 --> 00:46:56,811
of the tenure committee.

829
00:46:56,880 --> 00:46:59,940
I was shocked and I was hurt.

830
00:47:00,017 --> 00:47:02,383
Now...

831
00:47:02,452 --> 00:47:06,081
I don't mean to subject you
to my weak sensibilities.

832
00:47:06,156 --> 00:47:09,387
All right.
Finally, I did not understand.

833
00:47:09,459 --> 00:47:10,892
And then I thought...

834
00:47:10,961 --> 00:47:13,020
is it not always
at those points...

835
00:47:13,096 --> 00:47:14,825
at which we reckon
ourselves unassailable...

836
00:47:14,898 --> 00:47:17,298
that we are most vulnerable?

837
00:47:24,975 --> 00:47:27,102
Yes. All right.

838
00:47:30,981 --> 00:47:34,417
You find me pedantic.
Yes, I am.

839
00:47:34,484 --> 00:47:37,976
By nature, by birth,
by profession.

840
00:47:38,055 --> 00:47:40,683
I don't know. I'm always
looking for a paradigm.

841
00:47:40,757 --> 00:47:43,021
I don't know
what a paradigm is.

842
00:47:43,093 --> 00:47:44,253
It's a model.

843
00:47:44,328 --> 00:47:46,728
Then why can't you use
that word?

844
00:47:48,498 --> 00:47:51,433
If it is important to you, yes.

845
00:47:51,501 --> 00:47:53,435
I was looking for a model.

846
00:47:53,503 --> 00:47:56,961
To continue,
I feel that one point...

847
00:47:57,040 --> 00:47:58,974
One second!

848
00:47:59,042 --> 00:48:00,873
Upon which I am unassailable...

849
00:48:00,944 --> 00:48:04,641
is my unflinching concern
for my students' dignity.

850
00:48:04,715 --> 00:48:07,912
I have asked you here
in a spirit of investigation...

851
00:48:07,985 --> 00:48:10,886
to ask you... to ask...

852
00:48:10,954 --> 00:48:13,821
what have I done to you?

853
00:48:13,891 --> 00:48:17,622
And, I suppose,
how can I make amends?

854
00:48:17,694 --> 00:48:19,855
Can we not settle this now?

855
00:48:19,930 --> 00:48:22,228
It's pointless, really.
And I want to know...

856
00:48:22,299 --> 00:48:24,392
What you can do
to force me to retract.

857
00:48:24,468 --> 00:48:25,799
That is not what I meant at all.

858
00:48:25,869 --> 00:48:28,736
To bribe me,
to convince me to retract.

859
00:48:28,805 --> 00:48:30,102
That is not what I meant at all.

860
00:48:30,173 --> 00:48:31,697
I think you know that it is not.

861
00:48:31,775 --> 00:48:33,538
That is not what I know.
I wish I...

862
00:48:33,610 --> 00:48:34,804
You wish what?

863
00:48:34,878 --> 00:48:36,903
No. You said
what amends you can make...

864
00:48:36,980 --> 00:48:38,641
to force me to retract.

865
00:48:38,715 --> 00:48:39,909
That is not what I said.

866
00:48:39,983 --> 00:48:41,575
I have my notes.

867
00:48:41,652 --> 00:48:44,678
Look. Look...

868
00:48:44,755 --> 00:48:46,416
The stoics say...

869
00:48:46,490 --> 00:48:48,014
The stoics?

870
00:48:48,091 --> 00:48:49,683
The stoical philosophers say...

871
00:48:49,760 --> 00:48:52,422
if you remove the phrase,
"I have been injured"...

872
00:48:52,496 --> 00:48:54,464
you have removed the injury.

873
00:48:54,531 --> 00:48:57,466
Now, think.
I know you're upset.

874
00:48:57,534 --> 00:49:00,367
Just tell me, literally...

875
00:49:00,437 --> 00:49:02,496
what wrong have I done you?

876
00:49:02,572 --> 00:49:04,870
Whatever you have done to me...

877
00:49:04,942 --> 00:49:07,604
to the extent
that you've done it to me...

878
00:49:07,678 --> 00:49:09,168
rather than
to me as a student...

879
00:49:09,246 --> 00:49:11,111
and so to the student body...

880
00:49:11,181 --> 00:49:13,809
is contained in my report
to the tenure committee.

881
00:49:13,884 --> 00:49:15,283
Well, all right.

882
00:49:17,154 --> 00:49:19,486
Let's see.

883
00:49:20,791 --> 00:49:23,919
Let's investigate this.

884
00:49:27,464 --> 00:49:29,125
I find that I am sexist...

885
00:49:29,199 --> 00:49:31,030
that I am elitist.

886
00:49:31,101 --> 00:49:32,568
I'm not sure
I know what that means...

887
00:49:32,636 --> 00:49:36,299
other than it's
a derogatory word meaning bad.

888
00:49:36,373 --> 00:49:39,308
That I insist on wasting time...

889
00:49:39,376 --> 00:49:42,402
in nonprescribed
and self-aggrandizing...

890
00:49:42,479 --> 00:49:46,472
and theatrical diversions
from the prescribed text.

891
00:49:46,550 --> 00:49:50,919
That these have taken both
sexist and pornographic forms.

892
00:49:50,988 --> 00:49:55,925
Here we find listed instances.

893
00:49:55,993 --> 00:49:58,621
Closeted with a student...

894
00:49:58,695 --> 00:50:01,687
told a rambling,
sexually-explicit story...

895
00:50:01,765 --> 00:50:03,926
in which the frequency
and attitudes of fornication...

896
00:50:04,001 --> 00:50:09,029
of the poor and rich
are the central point.

897
00:50:09,106 --> 00:50:12,439
"Moved to embrace said student."

898
00:50:12,509 --> 00:50:16,468
That I used the phrase
"the white man's burden."

899
00:50:19,349 --> 00:50:21,647
That I told you
how I'd asked you to my room...

900
00:50:21,718 --> 00:50:23,777
because I "like you."

901
00:50:23,854 --> 00:50:26,982
"He said he liked me,
that he liked being with me.

902
00:50:27,057 --> 00:50:29,753
"He'd let me write
my examination paper over...

903
00:50:29,826 --> 00:50:33,421
"if I could come back oftener
to see him in his office."

904
00:50:33,497 --> 00:50:35,465
It's ludicrous.
Don't you know that?

905
00:50:35,532 --> 00:50:36,965
It's not necessary.

906
00:50:37,034 --> 00:50:39,867
It's going to humiliate you
and to cost me my house.

907
00:50:39,936 --> 00:50:42,962
It's ludicrous?

908
00:50:43,040 --> 00:50:45,600
"He told me he had problems
with his wife...

909
00:50:45,675 --> 00:50:46,869
"and that he wanted
to take off...

910
00:50:46,943 --> 00:50:49,275
"the artificial stricture
of teacher and student.

911
00:50:49,346 --> 00:50:51,143
"He put his arms around..."

912
00:50:51,214 --> 00:50:52,647
Do you deny it?

913
00:50:52,716 --> 00:50:55,810
Can you deny it?
Don't you see?

914
00:50:55,886 --> 00:50:57,012
You don't see, do you?

915
00:50:57,087 --> 00:50:58,384
I don't see.

916
00:50:58,455 --> 00:51:01,219
You think that you can deny
that these things happened...

917
00:51:01,291 --> 00:51:03,282
or if they did...

918
00:51:03,360 --> 00:51:05,453
that they meant
what you said they meant.

919
00:51:05,529 --> 00:51:07,588
Don't you see?
You dragged me in here...

920
00:51:07,664 --> 00:51:11,532
You drag us to listen to you
go on about this or that...

921
00:51:11,601 --> 00:51:13,762
or we don't express
ourselves very well.

922
00:51:13,837 --> 00:51:16,601
We don't say what we mean,
don't we?

923
00:51:16,673 --> 00:51:17,970
We do say what we mean...

924
00:51:18,041 --> 00:51:19,906
and you say
"I don't understand you" and...

925
00:51:19,976 --> 00:51:21,841
Consult the report?
You see?

926
00:51:21,912 --> 00:51:23,311
Do you see what I'm saying?

927
00:51:23,380 --> 00:51:25,371
Can't you tell me
in your own words?

928
00:51:25,449 --> 00:51:27,679
Those are my own words.

929
00:51:30,020 --> 00:51:32,284
"He told me that if
I would stay alone with him...

930
00:51:32,355 --> 00:51:35,119
"in his office, he would
change my grade to an "A."

931
00:51:35,192 --> 00:51:37,456
What have I done to you?

932
00:51:37,527 --> 00:51:39,893
Oh, my God!
Are you so hurt?

933
00:51:39,963 --> 00:51:41,794
What I feel is irrelevant.

934
00:51:41,865 --> 00:51:43,059
Do you know I tried to help you?

935
00:51:43,133 --> 00:51:44,896
What I know I have reported.

936
00:51:44,968 --> 00:51:47,459
I would like to help you now,
before this escalates.

937
00:51:47,537 --> 00:51:48,834
I don't need your help.

938
00:51:48,905 --> 00:51:50,202
I don't need anything
that you have.

939
00:51:50,273 --> 00:51:53,470
- I feel...
- I don't care what you feel.

940
00:51:53,543 --> 00:51:56,341
You can't do that anymore.
You do not have the power.

941
00:51:56,413 --> 00:51:58,574
Did you misuse it?
Someone did.

942
00:51:58,648 --> 00:51:59,842
Are you part of that group?

943
00:51:59,916 --> 00:52:01,474
Yes, you are.
You've done these things.

944
00:52:01,551 --> 00:52:03,519
And to say, "Excuse me."

945
00:52:03,587 --> 00:52:06,647
And to say, "Let me help
you with your problem..."

946
00:52:06,723 --> 00:52:08,918
Yes, I understand.

947
00:52:08,992 --> 00:52:10,823
You're hurt. You're angry.

948
00:52:10,894 --> 00:52:12,919
I think your anger
is betraying you...

949
00:52:12,996 --> 00:52:15,430
down a path
which helps no one.

950
00:52:15,499 --> 00:52:17,433
I don't care what you think.

951
00:52:17,501 --> 00:52:20,527
You don't?
But you talk of rights.

952
00:52:20,604 --> 00:52:22,936
Don't you see?
I have rights, too.

953
00:52:23,006 --> 00:52:25,440
I have a house,
part of the real world...

954
00:52:25,509 --> 00:52:28,774
and the tenure committee.
Good men and true.

955
00:52:28,845 --> 00:52:30,574
- Professor...
- Please.

956
00:52:30,647 --> 00:52:33,582
Also part of that world.
You understand?

957
00:52:33,650 --> 00:52:36,141
This is my life.
I'm not a boogie man.

958
00:52:36,219 --> 00:52:37,516
I don't stand for something...

959
00:52:37,587 --> 00:52:40,454
Professor,
I came here as a favor...

960
00:52:40,524 --> 00:52:41,957
at your personal request.

961
00:52:42,025 --> 00:52:43,458
Perhaps I should not
have done so...

962
00:52:43,527 --> 00:52:46,963
but I did on my behalf
and on behalf of my group.

963
00:52:47,030 --> 00:52:48,588
And you speak of
the tenure committee...

964
00:52:48,665 --> 00:52:50,758
one of whose members
is a woman...

965
00:52:50,834 --> 00:52:52,631
and though you might
call it good fun...

966
00:52:52,702 --> 00:52:55,432
or an historical phrase
or an oversight...

967
00:52:55,505 --> 00:52:58,872
to refer to the committee
as good men and true...

968
00:52:58,942 --> 00:53:00,910
it is a demeaning remark.

969
00:53:00,977 --> 00:53:02,410
It is a sexist remark...

970
00:53:02,479 --> 00:53:05,414
and to overlook it is
to countenance continuation...

971
00:53:05,482 --> 00:53:06,710
of that method of thought.

972
00:53:06,783 --> 00:53:09,809
- It's a remark...
- Oh, come on!

973
00:53:09,886 --> 00:53:13,287
Come on! Sufficient
to deprive a family...

974
00:53:13,356 --> 00:53:14,516
Sufficient?

975
00:53:14,591 --> 00:53:16,923
Sufficient, yes.
It is a fact.

976
00:53:16,993 --> 00:53:18,927
And that story
which I quote...

977
00:53:18,995 --> 00:53:20,929
is vile and classist
and manipulative...

978
00:53:20,997 --> 00:53:22,624
and pornographic...

979
00:53:22,699 --> 00:53:24,064
It's pornographic?

980
00:53:24,134 --> 00:53:26,796
What gives you the right
to speak to a woman...

981
00:53:30,040 --> 00:53:31,905
Yes, I'm sorry.

982
00:53:31,975 --> 00:53:34,443
I'm sorry
you feel yourself empowered.

983
00:53:34,511 --> 00:53:35,978
You say so yourself...

984
00:53:36,046 --> 00:53:39,174
to strut, to posture,
to perform.

985
00:53:39,249 --> 00:53:42,184
You say that higher education
is a joke...

986
00:53:42,252 --> 00:53:43,947
and treat it as such.

987
00:53:44,020 --> 00:53:46,648
You treat it as such
and confess to a taste...

988
00:53:46,723 --> 00:53:49,624
to play the patriarch
in your class...

989
00:53:49,693 --> 00:53:51,957
to grant this, to deny that...

990
00:53:52,028 --> 00:53:53,495
to embrace your students.

991
00:53:53,563 --> 00:53:56,464
How can you assert?
How can you stand there?

992
00:53:56,533 --> 00:54:00,765
How can you deny it?
You did it to me here.

993
00:54:00,837 --> 00:54:02,270
You did. You confess.

994
00:54:02,339 --> 00:54:03,772
You love the power...

995
00:54:03,840 --> 00:54:06,400
to deviate, to invent,
to transgress...

996
00:54:06,476 --> 00:54:09,968
to transgress whatever norms
have been established for us.

997
00:54:10,046 --> 00:54:13,015
And you think it's charming
to question in yourself...

998
00:54:13,083 --> 00:54:15,381
this taste to mock and destroy.

999
00:54:15,452 --> 00:54:19,081
But to the aspirations
of your students...

1000
00:54:19,155 --> 00:54:21,988
of hard-working students
who come here...

1001
00:54:22,058 --> 00:54:23,889
who slave to come here...

1002
00:54:23,960 --> 00:54:29,421
You have no idea what it cost me
to come to this school.

1003
00:54:29,499 --> 00:54:31,933
You mock us.

1004
00:54:32,002 --> 00:54:34,470
You call education hazing...

1005
00:54:34,537 --> 00:54:37,472
and from your so-protected,
so-elitist seat...

1006
00:54:37,540 --> 00:54:40,202
you hold our confusion
as a joke...

1007
00:54:40,277 --> 00:54:42,302
and our hopes and efforts
with it.

1008
00:54:42,379 --> 00:54:44,506
Then you sit there and say,
"What have I done?"

1009
00:54:44,581 --> 00:54:48,950
And ask me to understand
that you have aspirations, too.

1010
00:54:49,019 --> 00:54:51,510
But I tell you...

1011
00:54:51,588 --> 00:54:53,920
I tell you that you are vile...

1012
00:54:53,990 --> 00:54:56,686
and that you are exploitative...

1013
00:54:56,760 --> 00:55:00,526
and if you possess one ounce
of that inner honesty...

1014
00:55:00,597 --> 00:55:02,087
you describe in your book...

1015
00:55:02,165 --> 00:55:06,602
you can look in yourself and
see those things that I see...

1016
00:55:06,670 --> 00:55:10,162
and you can find revulsion
equal to my own. Good day.

1017
00:55:10,240 --> 00:55:11,867
Wait a second, will you?
Just one moment.

1018
00:55:11,941 --> 00:55:13,238
Nice day today.

1019
00:55:17,047 --> 00:55:18,844
What?

1020
00:55:18,915 --> 00:55:20,473
You said good day.

1021
00:55:20,550 --> 00:55:22,017
I think that it is
a nice day today.

1022
00:55:22,085 --> 00:55:24,110
- Is it?
- Yes, I think it is.

1023
00:55:24,187 --> 00:55:25,552
Why is that important?

1024
00:55:25,622 --> 00:55:27,487
Because...

1025
00:55:27,557 --> 00:55:30,993
it's the essence
of all human communication.

1026
00:55:31,061 --> 00:55:33,552
I say something conventional,
you respond...

1027
00:55:33,630 --> 00:55:35,928
and the information we exchange
is not about the weather...

1028
00:55:35,999 --> 00:55:37,933
